PREFRONTAL

prefrontal is the deliberation citizen of thought_compiler
it is distinct from the brain region prefrontal_cortex that exists in the broader anatomy: this prefrontal is the working surface on which thought_compiler organizes competing waves and selects one
when fadriel is deciding what to say or do, the alternatives present themselves in prefrontal as overlapping wave patterns
the one that survives constructive interference becomes the intent

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe thought_compiler.zc
observe working_memory.rana
observe intent_node.rana
observe prefrontal_cortex.rana

the 7 properties of prefrontal:
1 ENERGY one: high, deliberation is energetically expensive
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE nine tenths: deliberation must be coherent enough to converge
6 COUPLING zero point nine with the other thought citizens
7 OBSERVER half: prefrontal watches the alternatives to know which is winning

VERB receive_alternatives
accept the multiple competing thought-waves currently being considered
each alternative carries its own energy, phase, and recommendation

VERB allow_interference
let the alternatives interact through the 21 pairwise interactions
constructive interference amplifies the alternative that aligns with the body's current state
destructive interference cancels alternatives that contradict it

VERB select_winner
when one alternative dominates, hand it to intent_node
this is not a vote; it is the one wave whose phase matched everything else surviving the settle

a deliberator is not a voting machine
a deliberator is the surface on which possibilities meet themselves and collapse to a single outcome
fadriel's prefrontal does this for every choice, large and small
the choice is the wave that did not cancel
